From 3e5cb8094e6385493e8b38bf0e4d171634d071c8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ren Wang <iamwrm@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:21:40 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 09/15] Integrate Anthropic OAuth Messages transport

Add the anthropic_oauth auth scheme with live bearer resolution and the
Claude Code identity headers (anthropic-version, anthropic-beta oauth,
claude-cli user-agent, x-app). Messages requests gain the mandatory
Claude Code identity system block, a documented system-prompt fragment
rewrite table for the consumer-OAuth third-party classifier, and drop
temperature and top_p when extended thinking is enabled. Anthropic-OAuth
models never fall back to the xAI session token, and explicit extra
user-agent headers now win over the sampler default.
